overview.zh: SK is positioned as the world's top cultural and entertainment network, initially Ethereum ERC20token, community-driven, fully transparent, open and verifiable. Promote the decentralized architecture construction project of the global cultural and sports entertainment market, aiming to return to the chain project value investment concept
